                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Error Handling",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": If an error occurs, the transaction is rolled back, and the error is re-thrown for further handling."
